sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User
    participant MobileApp
    participant AttendanceFlow
    participant LocalStore as Hive
    participant RTDB as Firebase RTDB

    User->>MobileApp: Scan QR code
    MobileApp->>AttendanceFlow: handleScan(rollNo)
    AttendanceFlow->>LocalStore: get student by rollNo
    alt Local hit
        LocalStore-->>AttendanceFlow: student profile
    else Local miss
        AttendanceFlow->>RTDB: fetch studentsByRoll/{rollNo}
        RTDB-->>AttendanceFlow: student profile/null
        AttendanceFlow->>LocalStore: cache student (if found)
    end
    AttendanceFlow->>LocalStore: record entry/exit attendee
    AttendanceFlow-->>MobileApp: scan outcome + message
    MobileApp-->>User: success/blocked/invalid feedback
